What is UML?
		Graphical notation family
		backed by a meta-model
		helps describe and design software systems (mainly ones built using OO)

Ways of using UML
		1. Sketch
				- Communicate ideas and alternatives
				- Only important issues, not code details

		2. Blueprint
				Forward enginerring and reverse engineering
				Should be done using CASE
				Detailed
		3. Programming language

MDA
		Standard approach to using UML as a programming language
		PIM and PSM

Essence of UML are meta-models, not diagrams

